USERS (employees)
----------------
id (PK)
email
password_hash
full_name
has_yard_parking (boolean)
has_garage_card (boolean)

PARKING_SPOTS
----------------
id (PK)
type (YARD | GARAGE)
owner_user_id (FK users.id)

ABSENCES
----------------
id (PK)
parking_spot_id (FK)
date_from
date_to
created_at

RESERVATIONS
----------------
id (PK)
parking_spot_id (FK)
reserved_by_user_id (FK)
reservation_date
created_at
status (ACTIVE | CANCELLED | AUTO_RELEASED | EXPIRED)
